{"tid":1784120,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯國報告︰智利濫暴警應受檢控","createTime":"2019-12-15T12:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T13:12:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a419806601cbe14b4be7d6f5b9a125dc918b40bd","tid":1784120,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:16:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20191215/XUKHYT44ZH76MAYFKSWRJ65KBI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191215%2FXUKHYT44ZH76MAYFKSWRJ65KBI%2F&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hgp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=4a95d75c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191215%2FXUKHYT44ZH76MAYFKSWRJ65KBI%2F&h=c82e5bad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20191215/XUKHYT44ZH76MAYFKSWRJ65KBI/</a><br />\n<br />\n聯國報告︰智利濫暴警應受檢控<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191215/large/1576338238_a085.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191215%2Flarge%2F1576338238_a085.jpg&h=dad483c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聯合國人權事務高級專員辦公室前日發表智利人權報告，指當地兩個月來因地鐵加價而起的示威衝突中，軍警嚴重違犯人權和用武過度（圖），又涉非法殺人和酷刑，應受檢控。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n350示威者眼面中槍<br />\n<br />\n聯國人員10月30日至11月22日派員到智利調查，「有理據相信人權被嚴重侵犯」；約350名示威者眼睛或面部遭軍警以膠彈、催淚彈及彈殼近距離擊傷；殺傷力較低的武器「不當及不分對象」用於鎮壓和平示威者，未按照國際原則避免傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n調查又錄得軍警涉24宗性暴力和113宗虐打，又疑精神虐待拘留者，例如模擬處決及威嚇他們會被消失。報告指「很多案例在沒有監錄系統的地方發生，無從辨別施暴者身份」，促智利政府訂措施監察軍警操守，及要識別到身份。<br />\n<br />\n智利司法部人權副部長雷卡巴倫回應，當局仍在調查和懲治犯案者，聯國定論下得太早，「在我國政府看來未能充份反映事實，或有資料失誤」，又說派兵是因為有街頭暴力，並不是針對和平示威者。就射眼指控，智利以衞生部報告反駁，稱239名傷者中「只有」16人徹底喪失一邊眼睛視力。曾任智利總統的聯合國人權事務高級專員巴切萊特，上月底曾去信本港英語報章，促查反送中警暴。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"63eeffaadbda0de07c5f32f8f9cfb458d65b6127","tid":1784120,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDHdKiw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDHdKiw.jpg&h=779c8437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d19ec6c116b7ac8bf3bb97a50de7a77c0c0240c4","tid":1784120,"uid":41116,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:19:52.000Z","msg":"奶支那屎忽窿啦UN"},{"pid":"ac416baab668103d5639d61cc8a41390dd44e0a1","tid":1784120,"uid":88032,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:20:40.000Z","msg":"搞智利都唔搞香港<br />\n選擇性執法"},{"pid":"9db4231021ba161d44572246c56d86cd515d719b","tid":1784120,"uid":85116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:21:53.000Z","msg":"香港並唔係地球一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa6441dea2cddecfbe836b2faacea7402de3b49","tid":1784120,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:22:04.000Z","msg":"中共轄下機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb02050c1f16559cdaf3aa0b5f93ad819c290c7f","tid":1784120,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:29:35.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">德國戰線要人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"98111beb8f03158c988460558a0fbc1e71c323f1","tid":1784120,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:31:48.000Z","msg":"Lan 啦 UN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74ba9553feb